## 8. Conclusion

The Cross-Modal Convergence Rule is essential for eliminating hallucination, stabilizing deep reasoning, maintaining safe multimodality, enabling AGI-class coherence, and synchronizing perception with narrative.

**It guarantees one world, one arc, one coherent mind.**
